<h4>How will you get a car?</h4>
<div class="housing-choice">
	<<link "Buy a car on your own">><<goto "AreaFocusedBuyAlone">><</link>>
	<p><em>Purchase a used car for $1,600. It's expensive and will take most of your savings, plus you'll need insurance and registration. But it's yours alone - you can use it whenever you need, make all decisions about it, and don't have to coordinate with anyone else.</em></p>
</div>
<hr>
<div class="housing-choice">
	<<link "Find another family to share the cost">><<goto "AreaFocusedCarShare">><</link>>
	<p><em>Reach out to your network at the shelter and find another immigrant family that also needs a car. Split the $1,600 cost - you each pay $800. You'll have to coordinate schedules and share usage, but it makes car ownership much more affordable. Plus you'll build community ties.</em></p>
</div>

:: AreaFocusedBuyAlone
<<set $step = 0>><<ShowInfo>>
<h3>Solo Purchase</h3>
<div class="consequence-text">
	<p>You decide to buy the car on your own. It's a 2008 Honda Civic with 165,000 miles. The engine runs rough and the paint is faded, but mechanically it's sound. The seller wants $1,600 cash.</p>
	<p>You negotiate down slightly but not much - everyone knows cars are expensive right now. You pay $1,600 for the car, another $150 for insurance, and $100 for registration and title transfer.</p>
	<p>It takes almost all your savings, but when you drive it home for the first time, you feel something you haven't felt in months: freedom.</p>
	<p>No more waiting for rideshares. No more expensive trips adding up. No more being limited to one neighborhood. The city is yours to work in now.</p>
	<p>Your wife smiles when she sees it. "Now you can go anywhere," she says.</p>
	<p>And she's right. Your business is about to change completely.</p>
</div>
<hr>
<div class="success-box">
	<p style="color: green;"><strong>Success:</strong> You own a car outright. Your transportation costs will drop dramatically, and you can take jobs anywhere in the city without restrictions.</p>
</div>
<<link "Continue to day choice">><<goto "AFBA1">><</link>>

